summary: Memo for the record documenting a discussion between SR Division members and the CoS Helsinki concerning the timetable of Lee Harvey Oswald's stay in Finland and Helsinki in October 1959, including his contact with the Soviet Consulate. The discussion includes details on travel times, consulate hours, and airport passenger list retention policies.
title: DISCUSSION between members SR Division, and CoS Helsinki concerning timetable OF OSWALD'S stay in Finland and Helsinki
